<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Creative Landing Page</title>

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;
}

html{
    scroll-behavior:smooth;
}

body{
    background:#f5f7ff;
    color:#333;
}

/* Navigation */

header{
    position:fixed;
    width:100%;
    top:0;
    left:0;
    background:#fff;
    box-shadow:0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.1);
    z-index:1000;
}

nav{
    width:90%;
    margin:auto;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    align-items:center;
    padding:18px 0;
}

.logo{
    font-size:30px;
    color:#4f46e5;
    font-weight:bold;
}

nav ul{
    display:flex;
    list-style:none;
}

nav ul li{
    margin-left:25px;
}

nav ul li a{
    text-decoration:none;
    color:#333;
    font-weight:bold;
    transition:.3s;
}

nav ul li a:hover{
    color:#4f46e5;
}

button{
    padding:12px 24px;
    border:none;
    background:#4f46e5;
    color:white;
    border-radius:30px;
    cursor:pointer;
    transition:.3s;
}

button:hover{
    background:#312e81;
}

/* Hero */

.hero{
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    align-items:center;
    min-height:100vh;
    padding:120px 10%;
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,#eef2ff,#dbeafe);
}

.hero-text{
    width:50%;
}

.hero-text h1{
    font-size:60px;
    margin-bottom:20px;
}

.hero-text p{
    font-size:20px;
    line-height:1.7;
    margin-bottom:35px;
}

.btn{
    display:inline-block;
    padding:15px 35px;
    background:#4f46e5;
    color:white;
    border-radius:30px;
    text-decoration:none;
    transition:.3s;
}

.btn:hover{
    background:#312e81;
}

.hero-image{
    width:40%;
    text-align:center;
    font-size:180px;
}

/* Features */

.features{
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    gap:30px;
    padding:90px 10%;
    background:white;
}

.card{
    background:#eef2ff;
    padding:40px;
    border-radius:15px;
    width:300px;
    text-align:center;
    transition:.4s;
}

.card:hover{
    transform:translateY(-10px);
    box-shadow:0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.15);
}

.card h3{
    color:#4f46e5;
    margin-bottom:15px;
}

/* About */

.about{
    padding:90px 10%;
    text-align:center;
}

.about h2{
    font-size:42px;
    margin-bottom:20px;
}

.about p{
    max-width:800px;
    margin:auto;
    font-size:20px;
    line-height:1.8;
}

/* CTA */

.cta{
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,#4f46e5,#7c3aed);
    color:white;
    text-align:center;
    padding:90px 10%;
}

.cta h2{
    font-size:42px;
    margin-bottom:25px;
}

.cta button{
    background:white;
    color:#4f46e5;
    font-weight:bold;
}

/* Footer */

footer{
    background:#111827;
    color:white;
    text-align:center;
    padding:25px;
}

/* Responsive */

@media(max-width:768px){

.hero{
    flex-direction:column;
    text-align:center;
}

.hero-text,
.hero-image{
    width:100%;
}

.hero-image{
    margin-top:40px;
    font-size:120px;
}

.features{
    flex-direction:column;
    align-items:center;
}

nav ul{
    display:none;
}
}
</style>

</head>

<body>

<header>

<nav>

<div class="logo">Creative.</div>

<ul>
<li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
<li><a href="#features">Features</a></li>
<li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
<li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
</ul>

<button onclick="welcome()">Get Started</button>

</nav>

</header>

<section class="hero" id="home">

<div class="hero-text">

<h1>Build Amazing Websites</h1>

<p>
Create stunning and responsive websites using HTML, CSS and JavaScript.
Perfect for beginners to showcase their creativity.
</p>

<a href="#features" class="btn">Explore More</a>

</div>

<div class="hero-image">
💻
</div>

</section>

<section class="features" id="features">

<div class="card">
<h3>Responsive</h3>
<p>Works beautifully on desktop, tablet and mobile devices.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Modern UI</h3>
<p>Clean layout with attractive colors, shadows and animations.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Fast Performance</h3>
<p>Optimized code for a smooth and fast browsing experience.</p>
</div>

</section>

<section class="about" id="about">

<h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>

<p>
We design clean, responsive and user-friendly websites using modern web
technologies. This landing page demonstrates HTML, CSS and JavaScript
skills with an elegant and professional interface.
</p>

</section>

<section class="cta" id="contact">

<h2>Ready to Build Something Great?</h2>

<button onclick="welcome()">Join Now</button>

</section>

<footer>

<p>© 2026 Creative Landing Page | Designed with ❤️ using HTML, CSS & JavaScript</p>

</footer>

<script>
function welcome(){
    alert("Welcome! Thanks for visiting our Landing Page.");
}

console.log("Landing Page Loaded Successfully");
</script>

</body>
</html>
